OL,3,CPoliticians vote to increase public
OL,4,Cfunding for IVF treatment
OL,6,FPeople in are a step closer to
OL,7,Freceiving more money from the
OL,8,Fgovernment to help pay for up to three
OL,9,Fcycles of IVF treatment.
OL,11,FThe current support , leaving the vast
OL,12,Fmajority with thousands of pounds in
OL,13,Fmedical bills.
OL,15,FDeputy Lucy Stephenson, whose second
OL,16,Fson was born with the help of IVF,
OL,17,Fargues "the current eligibility
OL,18,Fcriteria is so low that there is no
OL,19,Fevidence anyone has ever qualified"
OL,20,Fand lodged a proposition calling for a
OL,21,Fbetter funding model.
