OL,3,CPoliticians vote to increase public
OL,4,Cfunding for IVF treatment
OL,6,FIt was eventually supported
OL,7,Foverwhelmingly as politicians voted 44-
OL,8,F1 in favour but only after Deputy Tom
OL,9,FBinet's amendment was included.
OL,11,FThat means rather than automatically
OL,12,Fadopting NICE clinical guidance that
OL,13,Fwould see all women under 40 given up
OL,14,Fto three IVF cycles paid for fully by
OL,15,Ftaxpayers, there will now be a
OL,16,Fconsultation over who can qualify and
OL,17,Fhow much is covered.
