OL,6,FPosting on social media after the
OL,7,Fvote, Deputy Stephenson said:
OL,8,F"Disappointingly, the Assembly adopted
OL,9,Fan amendment from the Health Minister
OL,10,Fwhich watered down my original
OL,11,Fproposal somewhat and we now need to
OL,12,Fwait and see what improvement looks
OL,13,Flike to this government."
OL,15,FOfficial figures show Jersey's
OL,16,Ffertility rate between 2020 and 2022
OL,17,Fwas among the lowest in the world at
OL,18,F1.3.
