OL,6,FIt was also the lowest figure for the
OL,7,Fisland in 27 years - a fertility rate
OL,8,Fof 2.1 is needed to maintain a stable
OL,9,Fpopulation.
OL,11,FHow does Jersey compare to other
OL,12,Fplaces?
OL,14,FJersey is understood to be the only
OL,15,Fplace in Europe to mean-test IVF
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,18,FGuernsey provides some financial help
OL,19,Fwith the cost of travel and medication
OL,20,Fbut treatment is not covered.
