OL,3,CPoliticians vote to increase public
OL,4,Cfunding for IVF treatment
OL,6,FIn the UK, NICE fertility clinical
OL,7,Fguidance states up to three cycles of
OL,8,FIVF should be offered for free through
OL,9,Fthe NHS to women under 40 if they have
OL,10,Fnot been able to get pregnant through
OL,11,Fregular unprotected sex and artificial
OL,12,Finsemination first.
OL,14,FWomen aged 40 to 42 are also eligible
OL,15,Ffor one cycle of free treatment as
OL,16,Flong as they meet certain health
OL,17,Fcriteria.
