OL,4,Cfunding for IVF treatment
OL,6,FScotland follows this but in England
OL,7,Fand Wales a final decision is made at
OL,8,Fa local level so as certain regional
OL,9,Fcare boards are stricter than others.
OL,11,FIn Wales, the Welsh Health Specialised
OL,12,FServices Committee sets the criteria
OL,13,Fand provides two full cycles for women
OL,14,Funder 40 and one for those aged 40-42.
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland announced in February
OL,17,Fthat it was improving its IVF
OL,18,Ffinancial support by offering one free
OL,19,Ffull cycle for those who qualify.
